doctype html
html
    head
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width')
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/index.css")
    body
        div(class="page-container")
          h1 🎢 RCDB Scraper 🎢 
          p This is a simple app that helps us scrape data from the uncooperative folks at rcdb. It currently works for coasters only.
          p Head to #[a(href="http://rcdb.com") rcdb] and create an #[a(href="https://rcdb.com/os.htm?ot=2") advanced search]. Grab the URL of the search results page and paste it into the input below, then hit Submit! A CSV of your results should start downloading.
          p For example, submitting https://rcdb.com/r.htm?ex=on&ol=18965&ot=2 will get you a CSV of every operating coaster in the great state of Pennsylvania.
          p It's a work in progress! You can #[a(href="mailto:willowceleste325@gmail.com") email me] if something is broken 😁 
          form(action="/coasters", method='GET' class="form") 
            input(type="text", name='url' placeholder="Enter rcdb search url" class="url-input")
            input(type='submit', value='Submit')
        div
          p(data-results)